URL: https://aj2duncan.github.io/thesisdownrli/, https://github.com/aj2duncan/thesisdownrli
BugReports: https://github.com/aj2duncan/thesisdownrli/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
SystemRequirements: pandoc (>= 1.18) - http://pandoc.org
Suggests: 
    testthat,
    covr,
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
